abstract: Retired Royal Air Force fighter jet performing at Shoreham Airshow in West Sussex, England, crashes into highway, killing seven people and injuring 15 others; pilot's fate is unknown.
lead_paragraph: A fighter jet taking part in a British airshow in West Sussex, on England’s southern coast, crashed into a busy road.

headline.main: 7 Dead as Fighter Jet Crashes Into Highway at British Airshow
